<% content_for :title, "teamhuddle | Find the sports you love playing, with the players you love playing with!" %>

<div class="container-fluid" ng-controller="landing-page" ng-cloak>

<div class="landing-page">

  <section class="header-outer col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
    <div class="header">
        <%= image_tag 'logo-compressed.png', class: "logo center-block", alt: 'teamhuddle_logo'%>
        <div class="text-center">
          <h1>teamhuddle</h1>
          <h4 class="intro">A platform connecting your community through sports</h4>
          <h3 class="slogan">Find the sports you love playing, with the players you love playing with!</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="mailer-outer">
    <div class="mailer col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
      <div class="mailer-inner text-center">
          <h4>Submit your e-mail below to receive front of the line access to our beta</h4>
          <br>
          
          <form ng-submit="submit()" ng-class="{ animateSlide: success && submitted && !processing }"> <!--ng-hide="success && submitted && !processing" -->
              <input type="email" ng-model="email" class="form-control"/>
              <input value="submit" type="submit" class="btn btn-info"/>
          </form>
          <br>

          <!-- Show this div while waiting for a response from the server -->
        <div class="text-center"  ng-show="processing">
          <%= image_tag("loading.gif", alt: "loading") %>
        </div>

        <!-- Show this div on success -->
          <div class="panel panel-success" ng-if="success && submitted && !processing">
              <p>Thanks for signing up, {{user.email}}!</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Show this div if there was an error -->
          <div class="panel panel-warn" ng-if="!success && submitted && !processing">
              <p>There was an error processing your request. Sorry!</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
  </section>

   <section class="feature-outer">
    <div class="feature col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
      <h1 class="text-center">teamhuddle features</h1><br>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 center-block">
        <%= image_tag 'feature-maps.png', class: "center-block img-responsive", alt: 'Maps Feature'%>
        <h2 class="text-center feature1">drop-in finder</h2>
        <p>Not sure when and where your closest drop-in is? We’ve got you covered! Our map and listings help you find drop-ins around your neighborhood. Browse by day and skill level to find out what, where and when you want to play. We’re making it easier for you to keep active!</p>
        <input value="try it now" type="submit" class="center-block btn btn-danger">

      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 center-block">
        <%= image_tag 'feature-users.png', class: "center-block img-responsive", alt: 'Maps Feature'%>
        <h2 class="text-center feature3">check-in</h2>
        <p>Plan ahead to make your next drop-in worthwhile. Know which ones are popular, or which ones have space for you and your group. Whether you’re an athlete perfecting his/her craft, or social butterfly who enjoys seeing and meeting new players, the check-in and comments will give you more insight on the drop-in. </p><br>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 center-block">
        <%= image_tag 'feature-finder.png', class: "center-block img-responsive", alt: 'Maps Feature'%>
        <h2 class="text-center feature2">find a player</h2>
        <p>Tired of paying penalties for lack of players? Never be short-benched again! “Find a Player” helps you choose the players you need. Find a sub for your league or familiar faces to do drop-ins with! Need a team to play on? Update your athletic profile (COMING SOON) and show what you have to offer!</p><br>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="sport_logos-outer">
    <h1 class="text-center">current sporting options </h1>
    <div class="sport-logos-inner">
      <div class="icon-outer">
        <a href="/dropin-finder/#volleyball">
          <div class="sport_logo icon2">
            <%= image_tag "http://www.placehold.it/1x1", class: "img-responsive" %>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/dropin-finder/#basketball">
          <div class="sport_logo icon1">
            <%= image_tag 'http://www.placehold.it/1x1', class: "img-responsive" %>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/dropin-finder/#hockey">
          <div class="sport_logo icon3">
            <%= image_tag 'http://www.placehold.it/1x1', class: "img-responsive" %>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/dropin-finder/#soccer">
          <div class="sport_logo icon4">
            <%= image_tag 'http://www.placehold.it/1x1', class: "img-responsive" %>
          </div>
        </a>
        <div class="sport_logo icon5">
          <%= image_tag 'http://www.placehold.it/1x1', class: "img-responsive" %>
        </div>
        <div class="sport_logo icon6">
          <%= image_tag 'http://www.placehold.it/1x1', class: "img-responsive" %>
        </div>
        <div class="sport_logo icon7">
          <%= image_tag 'http://www.placehold.it/1x1', class: "img-responsive" %>
        </div>
        <div class="sport_logo icon8">
          <%= image_tag 'http://www.placehold.it/1x1', class: "img-responsive" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>   
  </section>

</div>
